Class ProductionRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • stephenaranda24.ProductionRecord

  • public class ProductionRecord
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains all of the details for a production record such as the production number, the product Id, the serial number, date produced, products produced, and their item counts.
